27
00:02:29,480 --> 00:02:30,420
and another after that.

28
00:02:31,880 --> 00:02:32,720
Nancheng

29
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:36,240
is just one link in the warlord chaos.

30
00:02:42,640 --> 00:02:44,440
The peace we long for

31
00:02:44,580 --> 00:02:46,200
won't come so easily.

32
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:53,240
In times like these,

33
00:02:54,350 --> 00:02:55,400
