34
00:02:57,960 --> 00:02:59,680
clinging to petty obsessions

35
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:01,000
and stirring up storms.

36
00:03:07,440 --> 00:03:09,130
If we survive this time,

37
00:03:09,380 --> 00:03:10,960
I want to hold an acknowledgment ritual,

38
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:14,240
bring my brother Sheng home,

39
00:03:15,200 --> 00:03:16,380
and give him a rightful name.

40
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:21,280
Stop with these Western gadgets.

41
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:23,240
Why, Young Marshal?

42
00:03:24,920 --> 00:03:26,320
