45
00:03:47,920 --> 00:03:48,920
Why?

46
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:51,180
Because your father is a traitor.

47
00:03:51,480 --> 00:03:53,440
My father was framed.

48
00:03:53,440 --> 00:03:55,880
Dai Shiyao already found the evidence.

49
00:03:58,140 --> 00:03:59,280
You'll be carrying the weight

50
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:02,080
of 36 innocent lives of the Qin family

51
00:04:03,040 --> 00:04:05,280
and my lifelong hatred for you.

52
00:04:15,480 --> 00:04:16,320
Sheng,

53
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:18,600
I came to ask for a drink.

54
00:04:20,200 --> 00:04:21,280
Perfect timing.

55
00:04:22,130 --> 00:04:23,400
I have something to ask you.

56
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:26,160
Was there more
to the Qin family incident?

57
00:04:27,280 --> 00:04:28,760
Why was there no news about it at all

58
00:04:28,760 --> 00:04:30,080
when I sent people to Chongqing?

59
00:04:33,760 --> 00:04:35,120
Matters this confidential

60
00:04:35,990 --> 00:04:37,670
aren't for just anyone to know.

61
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:41,440
At this very moment,

62
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:44,430
you're still hung up

63
00:04:44,430 --> 00:04:46,230
on something already settled?

64
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:48,520
That's just ridiculous.

65
00:04:50,760 --> 00:04:51,800
That girl must've

66
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:53,440
confused you,

67
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:55,560
trying to fool you

68
00:04:56,160 --> 00:04:58,080
to clear her family's name.

69
00:05:03,040 --> 00:05:05,600
