79
00:05:29,320 --> 00:05:30,920
You're decisive in action

80
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:32,840
and know what's worth the fight.

81
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:36,360
You're the real one fit
to be the Marshal.

82
00:05:58,240 --> 00:05:59,080
Great-grandfather.

83
00:06:10,440 --> 00:06:11,480
What are you doing?

84
00:06:12,200 --> 00:06:14,040
What's the point

85
00:06:14,320 --> 00:06:15,400
of keeping a useless maid?

86
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:24,120
Dai Congling.

87
00:06:32,320 --> 00:06:34,280
None of this is about Dai Shiyao.

88
00:06:35,200 --> 00:06:36,120
It's all you.

89
00:06:36,400 --> 00:06:39,320
You should've died
with your parents that day.

90
00:06:41,400 --> 00:06:43,080
You're behind everything.

91
00:06:43,520 --> 00:06:45,600
You set up my father

92
00:06:46,170 --> 00:06:48,480
